or sub-groups of pupils such as FSM or EAL. </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">2</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">) </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">Comparisons</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> with the predecessor school in the </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">month before</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> closure</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">, often </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">affected by</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">demoralisation</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">, also </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">exaggered</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> improvement claims</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">; </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">comparisons </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">with earlier years</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> would h</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">ave been more </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">valid</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">. </span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:150%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt"><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">3</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">) </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">The </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">2007 National Audit Office report</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">had similar flaws</span><span style="font-family:Cambria; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="f